content:
The Context namespace is used to manage the sharing and consumption of business application data by using Context Service.

New Class: Manage the processes of a Context Service with the following methods:

* buildContext(input) - create a context
* deleteContext(input) - delete a context
* evictContextDefinition(input) - remove context definition from cache
* getContext(input) - retrieve context details
* getContextTranslation(input) - retrieve context mappings by target mapping ID
* persistContext(input) - persist current data or state of context
* queryRecordStatus(input) - query record status
* queryTags(input) - query a context by tags
* updateContextAttributes(input) - update attributes of a context
title: Salesforce Summer '24 Release Notes: Context Namespace
